This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and the use of emojis in social media platforms. The paper also uses a siamese network architecture, which is a popular technique in the field of deep learning for natural language processing. Additionally, the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CY (Computers and Society) as it involves the use of deep learning techniques and the study of the impact of emojis on social media communication.
